   <talk_paragraph index="n1625_young_loffy-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1625_young_loffy-1-a" mid="13" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Do you remember these?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Young Loffy$<BR>Hey look who's here. it's the kid who sees ghosts!<BR>What's that in your hands?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1625_young_loffy-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1625_young_loffy-1-b" mid="15" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You remember?!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Young Loffy$<BR>This is <FONT color=#a94407>Bakayev's Rum Barrel</FONT>. <BR>How can I forget the taste of a Bakayev! I always filled my cabin with barrels of this rum and drank until I couldn't differentiate hangover from sea sickness! </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1625_young_loffy-1-b" image="QN_Npc_ghost_hound.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1625_young_loffy-1-c" mid="17" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Hound is waiting for you.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Young Loffy$<BR>OH! This is <FONT color=#a94407>Hound</FONT>'s favourite mouse toy!<BR>That son of a b... ehem... that hound loved tearing this mouse toy apart as if he was a cat.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1625_young_loffy-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1625_young_loffy-1-d" mid="19" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Pirate Smith!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Young Loffy$<BR>I think you told me that several times already. But I still don't understand what it has got to do with me.<BR>And who asked you to bring me these things?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1625_young_loffy-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1625_young_loffy-1-e" mid="21" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What freedom?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Young Loffy$<BR>Smith... I see. That fool.<BR>He must still be thinking of going back to the ocean. But I'm not going back. I've already obtained the freedom that I was searching for.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1625_young_loffy-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1625_young_loffy-1-f" mid="23" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Is that true freedom?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Young Loffy$<BR>I was sick and tired of my life and thought I could throw everything away anytime... I wanted to go anywhere at all, but I always ended up at the same place.<BR>So I'm contented with my life now. My mind is at peace.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1625_young_loffy-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1625_young_loffy-1-g" mid="25" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You look totally sane now... </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Young Loffy$<BR>Well... Some might say that the process of pursuing freedom itself is freedom, but I don't know those difficult stuff. All I know is that the my journey ended the moment the door of the Monolith was opened.<BR.I don't know where Smith is now, but I hope he finds peace too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1625_young_loffy-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1625_young_loffy-2" mid="27" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yeah right...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Young Loffy$<BR>What are you talking about? I've always been sane!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1625_young_loffy-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
